Both can be ordered from Bullocks Wilshire. Cutaway, shirt, necktie and vest 
can be rented from Gary's Tux Shop. Valentino suit, $675; shirt, $50, and bow 
tie, $18, from Saks. Girls' dresses, $145 each, and wreaths, $35 each, by Susan 
