<P>
QUESTIONNAIRE RETURN DATE IS FEB. 10 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The deadline for returning questionnaires for the 18th annual survey of 
Southern Califonria residential construction by the Times real estate section 
is Feb. 10. 
</P>
<P>
Home builders in Los Angeles, Orange, San Diego, Riverside, San Bernardino, 
Kern and Ventura counties who have not received the mailed forms may obtain the 
single-sheet survey by calling 213/237-7349. 
</P>
<P>
The survey will gather information on sales volume and construction of homes, 
condominiums, apartments and inventory for 1988 and projections for 
construction and sales for 1989. 
</P>
