District seat, three challengers remain in the race against Councilman Zev 
Yaroslavsky. ; Photo, Laura M. Lake ROBERT GABRIEL / Los Angeles Times; Photo, 
Ryan Snyder CASSY COHEN / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Jack McGrath, below, who's 
seen in a 1984 photograph. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
