<P>
ANTI-HIJACKING SEMINAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NICOSIA, Cyprus 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Saudi Arabia will host an international conference in February on how to 
prevent airline hijackings, the Qatar News Agency said Friday. 
</P>
