<P>
Photo, Darren Matsubara, left, of CS Northridge breaks out of the pack after 
grabbing a rebound in the first half of a CCAA game Saturday at Cal Poly San 
Luis Obispo. ; Photo, Air show -- Bill Archer, left, fakes Derrick Gathers of 
Northridge into the air in the Matadors' 72-63 victory. See story, Page 30. 
GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
