<P>
Two firefighters who were part of a recent earthquake relief effort in Soviet 
Armenia will present slides and discuss their observations today at Armenian 
Apostolic Church of Orange County-Forty Martyrs in Santa Ana. Battalion Chief 
Mike McGroarty of the La Habra Fire Department and Division Chief Larry Greene 
of Fullerton will be joined by the guest speaker, Prof. Hovhannes Agajanian, 
chairman of the urology department at the Post-Graduate Institute of Yerevan, 
Armenia. 
